                  </h3>
                  <ol style="color:#475569; padding-left:18px; line-height:1.6;">
                    <li>Go to the password reset page</li>
                    <li>Enter the OTP shown above</li>
                    <li>Create a new strong password</li>
                  </ol>
                </div>

